    "Overall, the performance of Dictionary 3 (%DIFF measure) appears more robust to variations in preprocessing combinations.",
    "foot_12 SML methods In Fig. 9, we show the effects of data preprocessing on SML performance (excluding the transformer models with dedicated preparation pipelines).",
    "The performance of SML classification methods appears robust to different pre-processing combinations.",
    "While it does appear that lemmatization improves model performance in most cases, performance differences remain relatively small.",
    "In Appendix E, we discuss several additional pre-processing steps and alternative text representations and evaluate how they affect model performance."
